<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 Apr 2026 12:56:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美伊停火计划推动比特币升至三周高位</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/bitcoin-jumps-to-three-week-high-on-us-iran-ceasefire-plan</link><description>美国和伊朗达成停火协议后，全球市场变得更加乐观，比特币触及三周高点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igeBnNNJht2I/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 00:26:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/bitcoin-jumps-to-three-week-high-on-us-iran-ceasefire-plan</guid></item><item><title>价格暴跌令持有者不安，摩根士丹利推出比特币 ETF</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/morgan-stanley-debuts-bitcoin-etf-as-price-slump-rattles-holders</link><description>摩根士丹利将成为第一家推出自己的比特币追踪交易所交易基金的华尔街银行，这是数字资产生态系统的一个里程碑，凸显了原始加密货币已经深深融入金融主流——即使其周围的市场已经降温。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQiKNwsr62dE/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 12:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/morgan-stanley-debuts-bitcoin-etf-as-price-slump-rattles-holders</guid></item><item><title>白宫经济学家表示稳定币奖励不会损害银行</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/white-house-economists-says-stablecoin-rewards-won-t-harm-banks</link><description>白宫经济学家在周三的一份报告中表示，禁止加密货币公司向客户提供稳定币收益不会对社区银行产生有意义的影响，这标志着两个行业之间激烈冲突的最新进展，该冲突已导致国会立法陷入停滞。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV3Gy8fSExP4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/white-house-economists-says-stablecoin-rewards-won-t-harm-banks</guid></item><item><title>币安创始人回忆录详细介绍了 Gensler 早期的关系和入狱时间</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/binance-founder-s-memoir-details-early-gensler-ties-prison-time</link><description>赵长鹏在承认反洗钱和违反美国制裁的罪行之前，将币安打造成全球最大的加密货币交易所，他在周二出版的回忆录中讲述了他对该公司法律危机的看法。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iiSzNMP5yOyQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 01:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/binance-founder-s-memoir-details-early-gensler-ties-prison-time</guid></item><item><title>MrBeast 的数字化推动遭遇了持怀疑态度的伊丽莎白·沃伦 (Elizabeth Warren)</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-07/mrbeast-s-digital-push-runs-into-a-skeptical-elizabeth-warren</link><description>改善 YouTube 一代的财务未来。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/is41fjn3VToM/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-07/mrbeast-s-digital-push-runs-into-a-skeptical-elizabeth-warren</guid></item><item><title>中东紧张局势缓解后比特币收窄损失</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-07/bitcoin-slides-with-risk-assets-as-trump-s-iran-ultimatum-looms</link><description>尽管唐纳德·特朗普总统的关键停火期限临近，但随着投资者对外交解决中东冲突抱有希望，比特币减少了损失。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iT9YTH88rZiI/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 05:19:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-07/bitcoin-slides-with-risk-assets-as-trump-s-iran-ultimatum-looms</guid></item></channel></rss>